BuildTools      : ocamlbuild, camlp4
Homepage        : https://github.com/cakeplus/pa_where
OASISFormat     : 0.4
OCamlVersion    : >= 3.11

Description:
  Pa_where provides a syntax for backward declarations (allowing a
  top-to-bottom declarative style), using the "where" keyword.
  Local definitions in expressions and toplevel definitions are both supported.

Library pa_where
  Path: src
  Modules: Pa_where
  FindlibName: pa_where
  BuildDepends: camlp4.lib, camlp4.quotations, camlp4.extend
  CompiledObject: byte
  XMETAType: syntax
  XMETARequires: camlp4

